<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Workspace Invitation</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #111827; background: #f8fafc; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 640px; margin: 32px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); overflow: hidden; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #059669, #047857); color: #fff; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 0.2px; }
    .content { padding: 32px; }
    .content h2 { margin-top: 0; color: #0f172a; }
    .pill { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 14px; background: #ecfdf3; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0; color: #065f46; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; margin: 8px 0; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 22px; background: #059669; color: #fff !important; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin: 18px 0; font-weight: 600; }
    .button:hover { background: #047857; }
    .note { background: #f8fafc; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 14px; border-radius: 6px; margin-top: 16px; color: #475569; }
    .footer { background: #f1f5f9; padding: 18px; text-align: center; color: #64748b; font-size: 13px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>You're invited to {{workspaceName}}</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hello,</h2>
      <p>{{inviterName}} added you to <strong>{{workspaceName}}</strong>.</p>
      <p>Use the temporary password below to sign in and set your own password.</p>
      <div class="pill">Temporary password: {{tempPassword}}</div>
      <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Sign in</a>
      <p class="note">For security, this temporary password is valid for first login only. Please change your password after signing in.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Real-Time Pulse</p>
      <p>If you did not expect this invitation, you can ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
